      "name": "Grid convergence index validation for pump CFD mesh",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry. Grid Convergence Index (GCI) computed for velocity magnitude and wall shear stress at all impeller passages. GCI < 2% achieved on the fine mesh (16.4M cells), confirming discretisation error is within acceptable bounds for MRL 2.",
      "passFail": "Pass",
      "quantitativeResult": "GCI_fine = 1.7% for velocity; GCI_fine = 1.9% for WSS",
