      "name": "Hemolysis validation verification method requirement",
      "description": "Per the device submission plan and ASME V&V 40 Section 5.3, validation of the hemolysis CFD model against physical data must be performed using a controlled experiment in which pump operating parameters are systematically varied under defined, reproducible laboratory or bench conditions. Observational or registry-based data collection does not satisfy this requirement because confounding variables cannot be adequately controlled. The required verification method is therefore designated as controlled-experiment.",
      "requiredVerificationMethod": "controlled-experiment",
